leve.name: Creature Feature
leve.description: Camp Tranquil is far from that lately, with beasts of all sorts popping up everywhere but in the afternoon mug of barley soup. Some fear we are being softened up for an attack by enemies unknown. Such terrors being more harmful than an occasional imp in the outhouse, the infestation must be cleared out forthwith.
leve.client: The Order of the Twin Adder Blue Badgers
